{"tid":2230257,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"金融時報:前中國外交官曾擔任海外版TikTok全球內容審查主管","createTime":"2020-10-04T23:05:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T23:46:40.000Z","uid":204533,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"26250242efc6dbd6bbb9e3720109a320960d6478","tid":2230257,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T23:05:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>據英國《金融時報》網站報導，一名前中國駐伊朗外交官曾經在北京字節跳動公司擔任抖音海外版TikTok的全球內容審查部門主管的職務。<br />\n<br />\n該報導10月3日援引知情人士的話說，這位名為鄭才（音譯）的前外交官曾經在北京管理字節跳動的內容政策團隊。報導說，鄭才負責運行北京總部的全球信任與安全團隊，制定TikTok、Helo以及Vigo Video等國際應用程序的內容審查規定。<br />\n......<br />\n自<strong><span class=\"red\">今年1月，鄭才已經離開了這個職位</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。字節跳動發言人說，聘用他時&ldquo;並沒有考慮到他之前在公共部門的的角色，在招聘過程中也沒有與政府進行對話。&rdquo;<br />\n.......<br />\n2018年是字節跳動內容審查政策調整的關鍵一年。這一年，該公司旗下最受歡迎的新聞應用程序&ldquo;今日頭條&rdquo;的產品負責人被當局審查部門約談並被要求整改、&ldquo;內涵段子&rdquo;被整改關停，公司CEO張一鳴發表道歉公開信，表示為公司產品&ldquo;出現了與社會主義核心價值觀不符的內容&rdquo;負責。<br />\n<br />\n《金融時報》說，<strong><span class=\"red\">TikTok目前的內容審查調整工作主要由全球各地的地方團隊負責，但在某些情況下，決定標籤功能和有關推送視頻的算法的工程師主要都在北京和上海兩地。</span></strong><br />\n.......<br />\n英國《衛報》等媒體報導，TikTok這一全球應用平台審查多項被中國政府視為敏感的議題，<strong><span class=\"red\">包括西藏獨立、台灣獨立、香港民主示威活動、新疆維吾爾人維權、天安門事件和法輪功等。</span></strong></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/former-Chinese-diplomat-tiktok-content-policy/5608392.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Fa%2Fformer-Chinese-diplomat-tiktok-content-policy%2F5608392.html&d=A6Q0GQr%2FGmLii1x5qL7rGFTAjexNHzxSh3iQmMoU3XE%3D&h=6b7df286\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/a/former-Chinese-diplomat-tiktok-content-policy/5608392.html</a>"},{"pid":"4597e32a8eae716549f09c006c6d8781043f600a","tid":2230257,"uid":284432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T23:12:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"863cf9b71ec33b98089bb93e0b33e2e9e309fc16","tid":2230257,"uid":204533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4597e32a8eae716549f09c006c6d8781043f600a","tid":2230257,"uid":284432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T23:12:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T23:14:58.000Z","msg":"無知鬼佬表示: TIKTOK好好玩, 幫我搵好多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76a5d2240d077e9ff5ae9ecb77540749ce21bd58","tid":2230257,"uid":167956,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T23:16:44.000Z","msg":"搵鬼先信同共匪無關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"607ab50cb3b37d61001b94322580a4c5591baa0c","tid":2230257,"uid":54125,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T23:17:52.000Z","msg":"支那人台灣人香港人，人人都知<br />\n鬼佬就而家先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff27286039360f0bec4b8f379d69432db4105e37","tid":2230257,"uid":204533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"76a5d2240d077e9ff5ae9ecb77540749ce21bd58","tid":2230257,"uid":167956,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T23:16:44.000Z","msg":"搵鬼先信同共匪無關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T23:19:38.000Z","msg":"佢講得出請人個陣無留意佢官方背景個下先好笑<br />\n完全當人傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0e0f92edc646296306f861a71e28fb73266f1fc","tid":2230257,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T23:21:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f30d36c2fc5afcd371b292d13307ce909fa99b58","tid":2230257,"uid":167956,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ff27286039360f0bec4b8f379d69432db4105e37","tid":2230257,"uid":204533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"76a5d2240d077e9ff5ae9ecb77540749ce21bd58","tid":2230257,"uid":167956,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T23:16:44.000Z","msg":"搵